<li>Please forgive me.  I understand I’ve disappointed you, and I’ll do everything to earn back your trust.</li>
<li>My heart aches knowing I’ve upset you.  I’m truly sorry, and I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me.</li>
<li>I messed up, and I take full responsibility.  I love you, and I'm committed to making things right.</li>
